The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Double honour for Wie

Los Angeles: Michelle Wie had double cause to celebrate on Monday after receiving a special exemption for next months US Womens Open and her first invitation to play on the mens European Tour. 

The 16-year-old schoolgirl from Honolulu will compete in her 10th major championship at Newport Country Club on Rhode Island from June 29 to July 2. 

She will then play alongside the men for the ninth time in a professional event at the European Masters at Crans-sur-Sierre, Switzerland, from September 7-10. 

